reviewText:
Overall score
2/5
Just one step below good"

PROs
+ Simple mechanics;
+ Extended RPG development of units.

CONs
+ Bland looks and terrible music;
+ Shallow and repetitive tactics;
+ Lots of choices (RPG development) don't pay off;
+ History uncompelling.

Graphics and Audio 1/5
The looks of this game are quite unimpressive overall. There is not a distinctive look

